             were indicted for <rs id="t18200918-310-off1778" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-310-off1778" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-310-off1778" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-310-cd1779" type="crimeDate">25th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-310-off1778 t18200918-310-cd1779"></join>, 300 lbs. of lead, value 26 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-310-victim2819" type="victimName">
                           John Hinton 
                           Tritton
                        <interp inst="t18200918-310-victim2819" type="surname" value="Tritton"></interp>
